channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Oscar Mayer Wienermobile Crashes Along Chicago Area Highway
item.description: The hot dog-shaped vehicle hit a car Monday morning and its driver lost control and overcorrected, causing it to roll onto its side on I-294.

item.title: Baby's hair mysteriously falls out – then parents make horror discovery on home camera
item.description: A family were shocked by what they found after setting up a home security camera to try and find the source of a strange smell that led them to feel ill and saw their baby lose clumps of hair

item.title: Sharks ‘high on cocaine’ after drugs are being flushed down the loo
item.description: It could be affecting their behaviour making them more aggressive.

item.title: Gambling addict son filmed 'poisoning mother and stepfather so he could inherit their money'
item.description: Artyom Missyura, a gambling addict up to his neck in debt, reportedly admitted to trying to poison his family members to inherit their wealth

item.title: Psychic who envisioned Trump assassination attempt gives his US election prediction
item.description: 'I wasn't expecting this to happen until at least August this year.'

item.title: 'Short-tempered' cyclist jailed for life after stabbing BMW driver to death in road rage attack
item.description: Alexandros Josephs, who was an aspiring songwriter, was attacked by Ahmed Chakile Gonladieu who, the jury at the Old Bailey heard, was declared dead at the scene in Ladywell, southeast London

item.title: 14 children end up in hospital after trying ‘adult only’ crisps
item.description: The 'R18' crisps are made using an extract from the ultra-spicy ghost pepper.

item.title: Kamala Harris leads Trump in new poll as crowd chants 'lock him up' at rally
item.description: Kamala Harris visited the battleground state of Wisconsin on Tuesday where crowds chanted 'lock him up' after she highlighted Donald Trump's legal woes as she took the lead in a new poll

item.title: Woman describes out of body aura she felt in near-death experience after crash
item.description: 'The experience has allowed me to see the beauty of life.'

item.title: Moment hate preacher Anjem Choudary was caught by police in 'big step' for 'public protection'
item.description: Islamic radicaliser Anjem Choudary, 57, was found guilty of terror-related offences at Woolwich Crown Court on Tuesday in what was called a 'big step' towards 'public protection'
